### Anything else?

I tried use service insted function, I mean:

```
@Injectable({ providerIn: 'root' })
export class MyGuard {
  myService = inject(MyService)
  canActivate (...) {
    console.log(this.myService.propertyA) // Allways null
  }
}
```

I got same result

I tried to inject service on providers `app.config.ts`:
```
@Injectable()
export class MyService {
  propertyA: string | null
}
```
```
export const appConfig: ApplicationConfig = {
  providers: [
    ...
    MyService
  ]
}
```

I got same result

